name: Lysa TerKeurst
description: Live Loved.
tweets:
We can’t stop or control the things that come our way. And all of the unknowns can sometimes seem so frightening.
 
But we can make the minute-by-minute choice to let our souls rest in God. We don't have to understand; we just have to trust.

name: Lysa TerKeurst
description: Live Loved.
tweets:
You’re not who people say you are. You’re not who social media says you are. You’re not who the scale says you are. 

You’re who GOD says you are. And He says you're loved. He says you are held. He says You're His. 

Forever His.

name: Lysa TerKeurst
description: Live Loved.
tweets: While we are affected by other people’s actions, we are not held accountable for their actions. We are held accountable, though, for both our actions and our reactions.
